Package: targseq
Title: Tools for targeted sequencing analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fausto", "Rodriguez Zapata", email = "frodrig4@ncsu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for analyzing maize genetic data, creating phylogenetic trees, 
    and visualizing genetic variants. This package provides tools for sequence alignment processing,
    variant extraction, tree rotation, and advanced visualization with ggtree.
